text: One of the best Zhi Char stall around.Nice & yummy Salted Fish Fried Rice. Portion is generous too! Value for money!
Dine in and ordered the steam fish and the fish is very fresh. Now having promotion. $12.80 for whole fish… Valued for money.

Too bad, it's ok when there are no customers, but when there are a little more customers, the dishes are served out of order. I was the last one to order, but my food arrived after everyone else had finished eating.
